1:17:26.808 --> 1:17:28.810
-There's a woman.
-A woman?

1:17:30.479 --> 1:17:31.688
There's a weeping woman.

1:17:33.023 --> 1:17:34.066
When was that again?

1:17:35.150 --> 1:17:37.861
I was in the bathroom then too.

1:17:39.029 --> 1:17:41.031
I heard a woman crying somewhere.

1:17:42.199 --> 1:17:43.825
I looked around when I got out.

1:17:44.701 --> 1:17:49.581
A woman was crying,
up that field in the middle of her work.

1:17:51.833 --> 1:17:53.543
A woman crying?

1:17:54.378 --> 1:17:55.212
Yeah.

1:17:56.505 --> 1:17:57.923
