1:17:59.549 --> 1:18:00.884
It was a weird sight.

1:18:21.571 --> 1:18:22.447
Hi.

1:18:25.450 --> 1:18:26.284
Excuse me.

1:18:29.121 --> 1:18:30.580
Do you live here?

1:18:33.166 --> 1:18:34.042
