1:18:44.970 --> 1:18:46.638
Here, look.

1:18:46.722 --> 1:18:47.597
Police.

1:18:48.557 --> 1:18:49.391
Really?

1:18:49.474 --> 1:18:51.226
-Yeah--
-You can't be there.

1:18:52.477 --> 1:18:54.438
