1:20:25.362 --> 1:20:26.238
The same.

1:20:33.161 --> 1:20:34.621
You remember his face, right?

1:20:35.372 --> 1:20:39.709
I kept my face down
so I wouldn't see his face.

1:20:41.670 --> 1:20:43.380
Even with the panties over my head

1:20:44.881 --> 1:20:46.174
I kept my eyes shut.

1:20:48.093 --> 1:20:51.680
