he would've killed me.

1:20:54.891 --> 1:20:57.894
I don't know about anything else
but I do remember this.

1:20:59.646 --> 1:21:01.481
He had really soft hands.

1:21:02.899 --> 1:21:07.237
The hand that was covering my mouth
was pretty like that of a woman

1:21:07.904 --> 1:21:08.780
and soft.

1:21:43.023 --> 1:21:43.857
All set?

1:21:44.524 --> 1:21:45.817
Let's get some sleep now.

1:21:45.901 --> 1:21:46.860
RECORD OF TESTIMONY

1:21:46.943 --> 1:21:49.487
It'll be over when we stamp right here.

1:21:51.489 --> 1:21:52.741
Just as you testified.

1:21:54.159 --> 1:21:55.327
You like that, right?

1:21:55.410 --> 1:21:58.330
Yes, of course.

1:21:58.413 --> 1:22:02.083
So it's over now.

1:22:02.167 --> 1:22:03.668
Please let me down.

