1:30:18.496 --> 1:30:21.749
An Mi-seon's estimated time of death
is between 7:30 and 8:00 p.m.

1:30:21.833 --> 1:30:24.335
You ran out while listening to the radio.

1:30:24.419 --> 1:30:25.920
