1:30:26.003 --> 1:30:29.632
-Jo Yong-gu!
-Does this look like a joke, fucker?

1:30:29.715 --> 1:30:31.175
-Put him down.
-Stop it.

1:30:35.388 --> 1:30:36.264
Get behind me.

1:30:41.310 --> 1:30:42.186
You here.

1:30:43.229 --> 1:30:46.983
Even the kids know
you're torturing innocent men here.

1:30:47.066 --> 1:30:48.317
Shut the fuck up, you--

1:30:48.401 --> 1:30:49.610
Get over here!

1:30:53.948 --> 1:30:55.283
