there's no way you don't remember.

1:31:29.150 --> 1:31:31.402
So tell me, since you heard it all.

1:31:33.529 --> 1:31:34.405
I don't remember.

1:31:35.114 --> 1:31:36.157
You don't remember?

1:31:37.783 --> 1:31:39.452
